#: templates/public/home.html:13
msgid ""
"To claim the Ambassadors discount on the 4 Vallées annual pass, a returning "
"holder and a new holder have to apply together. We match you with a partner "
"automatically — no more scrambling in the Facebook group, no chasing people "
"who vanish."
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/home.html:22
msgid "Registration opens soon — check back closer to the start of the season."
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/home.html:30
msgid "How it works"
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/home.html:33
msgid "Register in the role that fits you — Ambassador or Referee."
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/home.html:35
msgid ""
"We add you to the queue and match you with a partner automatically. You "
"don't pick each other."
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/home.html:37
msgid "When you're matched, we email you. You have 72 hours to accept."
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/home.html:39
msgid ""
"Once you both accept, we share contact details so you can meet and apply "
"together."
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/home.html:47
msgid "Which one are you?"
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/home.html:52
msgid "I'm an Ambassador"
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/home.html:55
msgid ""
