#: templates/public/legal/terms.html:9
msgid "Last updated"
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/legal/cookies.html:11
msgid "What we use"
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/legal/cookies.html:13
msgid ""
"We only use strictly-necessary cookies: a session cookie to keep you signed "
"in, a security cookie to protect forms against cross-site request forgery, "
"and a cookie that remembers your chosen language."
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/legal/cookies.html:19
msgid "What we don't use"
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/legal/cookies.html:21
msgid ""
"We do not use analytics, advertising, or third-party tracking cookies, so "
"there is no cookie consent banner to manage."
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/legal/cookies.html:27
msgid "Managing cookies"
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/legal/cookies.html:29
msgid ""
"You can clear or block cookies in your browser settings, but the site will "
"not work correctly without the strictly-necessary cookies above."
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/legal/cookies.html:36
#: templates/public/legal/privacy.html:59
msgid ""
"This policy is a first-draft baseline and should be reviewed by a legal "
"professional before the program launches."
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/legal/privacy.html:4 templates/public/legal/privacy.html:8
msgid "Privacy Policy"
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/legal/privacy.html:11
msgid "Who we are"
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/legal/privacy.html:13
msgid ""
"This service matches partners for the 4 Vallées Ambassadors Program. The "
"data controller for the personal data processed here is Groupe Télé-Thyon "
"SA. For privacy questions, contact caissier@tele-thyon.ch."
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/legal/privacy.html:20
msgid "What we collect"
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/legal/privacy.html:22
msgid ""
"We deliberately collect only what matchmaking and contact require: your "
"name, email address, phone number, your role (Ambassador or Referee), your "
"chosen price category, your prior-season eligibility attestation, and your "
"preferred resort. We do not collect the full application details (date of "
"birth, address, photo ID, keycard, insurance) — those are handled off-app "
"when you apply in person."
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/legal/privacy.html:30
msgid "Why we use it"
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/legal/privacy.html:32
msgid ""
"We use your data to place you in the matching queue, pair you with a "
"partner, and let you contact each other once you have both accepted a match. "
"Your email and phone are never shown to another participant before you have "
"both accepted."
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/legal/privacy.html:39
msgid "How long we keep it"
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/legal/privacy.html:41
msgid ""
"We keep your data for the duration of the season you registered for and a "
"short period afterwards, then delete it. You can delete your account at any "
"time from your account page."
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/legal/privacy.html:48
msgid "Your rights (GDPR / Swiss FADP)"
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/legal/privacy.html:51
msgid ""
"You have the right to access, correct, export, or delete your personal data, "
"and to object to or restrict its processing. You can exercise most of these "
"directly from your account page, or by contacting us. You also have the "
"right to lodge a complaint with your data protection authority."
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/legal/terms.html:4 templates/public/legal/terms.html:8
msgid "Terms of Use"
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/legal/terms.html:11
msgid "What this service does"
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/legal/terms.html:13
msgid ""
"This service helps you find a partner for the 4 Vallées Ambassadors Program. "
"It is matchmaking only: the actual discount application and the purchase at "
"the ticket office happen separately, in person, and are not part of this "
"service."
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/legal/terms.html:20 templates/public/register_done.html:25
msgid "Your responsibilities"
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/legal/terms.html:22
msgid ""
"Give accurate information, including your honest prior-season eligibility."
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/legal/terms.html:23
msgid "Respond to a match within 72 hours — accept or decline."
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/legal/terms.html:25
msgid ""
"If you do not respond in time, your match is cancelled and you go to the "
"back of the queue."
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/legal/terms.html:29
msgid "Be respectful and prompt with the partner you are matched with."
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/legal/terms.html:32
msgid "Eligibility"
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/legal/terms.html:34
msgid ""
"Eligibility is self-declared here and verified off-app when you apply "
"together at the ticket office. Registering does not guarantee a match or "
"entitle you to the discount; both depend on the off-app application."
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/legal/terms.html:41
msgid "No guarantee"
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/legal/terms.html:43
msgid ""
"There are usually more referees than ambassadors, so we cannot guarantee "
"that everyone will be matched."
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/legal/terms.html:49
msgid ""
"These terms are a first-draft baseline and should be reviewed by a legal "
"professional before the program launches."
msgstr ""

